
<item rdf:about='http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xu-isis-service-sid-adv-00.txt'>
    <title>"Signaling Services and Service SIDs Using IS-IS", Xiaohu Xu</title>
    <link>http://www.ietf.org/internet-drafts/draft-xu-isis-service-sid-adv-00.txt</link>
    <description>The Segment Routing mechanism can be leveraged to realize the service path layer functionality of the Service Function Chaining (i.e, steering traffic through the service function path).  This document describes how to advertise services and the corresponding service segment IDs using IS-IS.</description>
    <dc:date>2014-04-22T07:00:00-00:00</dc:date>
</item>
